Package mars.venus

Class FileStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • mars.venus.FileStatus

  • public class FileStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to store and return information on the status of the current ASM file that is being edited in the program.
    Author:
    Team JSpim
